    <section xml:id="community-irc">
      <title>Internet Relay Chat - IRC</title>

      <para>Much of our conversations about Jetty occur on IRC in one location
      or another. Users are always welcome to come join our IRC channels and
      talk with us, other users, or just lurk.</para>

      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>irc.freenode.org - #jetty</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>Our primary location, we recommend that if your looking to
            find folks on IRC you try here.</para>

            <para>We also have commit notifications coming to this channel on
            the bottom and top of the hour.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>irc.codehaus.org - #jetty</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>Our prior location before the move to the eclipse
            foundation. We are idle on here.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </section>
